ont-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">、投标人资质要求：投标申请人必须是在中国境内注册，</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">具有有效的含家电生产或家电销售经营范围的营业执照，</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">有独立完成本项目所有工作的能力的独立法人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-fami